        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "epRUB",
          "name": "Article Body",
          "width": 1376,
          "gap": 24,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "4G7Ee",
              "name": "Content Column",
              "width": 900,
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 20,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "QvflG",
                  "name": "Intro Card",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "#FFFFFF",
                  "cornerRadius": 30,
                  "stroke": {
                    "align": "inside",
                    "thickness": 1,
                    "fill": "#E5E5EA"
                  },
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 18,
                  "padding": 28,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "2c9qD",
                      "name": "Intro Lead",
                      "fill": "#1D1D1F",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 820,
                      "content": "很多博客详情页的问题，不在于内容不够好，而在于信息被摆放得不够清楚。标题、导语、封面和正文之间如果没有稳定层级，读者会更快感到疲惫。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.55,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 20,
                      "fontWeight": "500"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "EhWwf",
                      "name": "Intro Body",
                      "fill": "#4D4D52",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 820,
                      "content": "所以在设计详情页时，我会优先处理三件事：让首屏就能建立主题印象；让正文阅读节奏稳定；让辅助信息存在但不喧宾夺主。这样的页面既像内容页面，也保留一点产品页的清晰感。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 17
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "pVQeE",
                  "name": "Section 1",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 16,
                  "padding": [
                    8,
                    0
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "1lujV",
                      "name": "Section Title",
                      "fill": "#1D1D1F",
                      "content": "1. 先决定读者第一眼看到什么",
                      "lineHeight": 1.1,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 30,
                      "fontWeight": "700"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "QRtev",
                      "name": "Section Body",
                      "fill": "#4D4D52",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 820,
                      "content": "如果首屏已经有大标题、导语和封面视觉，就不要再堆很多按钮、标签和花哨的说明。首屏的任务不是解释一切，而是建立一种‘可以安心读下去’的氛围。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 17
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "Ajdp2",
                      "name": "Section Body",
                      "fill": "#4D4D52",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 820,
                      "content": "在这版设计里，我保留了足够大的标题和柔和封面块，让首屏像一个轻量的内容海报。它不需要复杂，但必须足够明确。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 17
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "Em5wq",
                  "name": "Code Block Card",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "#F7F7FA",
                  "cornerRadius": 26,
                  "stroke": {
                    "align": "inside",
                    "thickness": 1,
                    "fill": "#E5E5EA"
                  },
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 12,
                  "padding": 24,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "RUugY",
                      "name": "Code Label",
                      "fill": "#0071E3",
                      "content": "CODE BLOCK",
                      "lineHeight": 1.3,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 12,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "ZKCW9",
                      "name": "Code Text",
                      "fill": "#1D1D1F",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 820,
                      "content": "## First impression\n\n- Keep the hero simple\n- Let spacing build hierarchy\n- Move secondary info into the sidebar\n\n> hierarchy before decoration",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "500"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "QdjHZ",
                  "name": "Quote Card",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "#F0F6FF",
                  "cornerRadius": 30,
                  "stroke": {
                    "align": "inside",
                    "thickness": 1,
                    "fill": "#D7E6FF"
                  },
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 12,
                  "padding": 26,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "DFoDT",
                      "name": "Quote Text",
                      "fill": "#1D1D1F",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 800,
                      "content": "“好的内容页不是把更多东西塞进去，而是帮读者更顺畅地走进去。”",
                      "lineHeight": 1.25,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 28,
                      "fontWeight": "700"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "q2ZEn",
                      "name": "Quote Meta",
                      "fill": "#0071E3",
                      "content": "Blockquote · rendered from markdown",
                      "lineHeight": 1.3,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 13,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "H0Sph",
                  "name": "Section 2",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 16,
                  "padding": [
                    8,
                    0
                  ],
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "2FkbK",
                      "name": "Section Title",
                      "fill": "#1D1D1F",
                      "content": "2. 让正文读起来像连续的体验，而不是信息清单",
                      "lineHeight": 1.1,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 30,
                      "fontWeight": "700"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "agFLZ",
                      "name": "Section Body",
                      "fill": "#4D4D52",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 820,
                      "content": "正文部分最怕碎。段落、标题、引用、侧栏信息都应该服务于阅读主线，而不是不断把注意力拉走。文章详情页的每一个模块，都应该有明确的存在理由。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 17
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "GjVx4",
                      "name": "Section Body",
                      "fill": "#4D4D52",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 820,
                      "content": "因此我通常会把正文控制在单一主列里，把作者信息、目录和订阅入口放到侧栏。这样读者既能快速定位，也不会被迫频繁切换视线轨迹。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 17
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "RvbMe",
                      "name": "Section Body",
                      "fill": "#4D4D52",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 820,
                      "content": "如果页面还有相关推荐，它更适合放在正文底部，作为完成阅读后的下一步，而不是提前挤进阅读路径里。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 17
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "cCDzA",
                  "name": "List Block Card",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "#FFFFFF",
                  "cornerRadius": 26,
                  "stroke": {
                    "align": "inside",
                    "thickness": 1,
                    "fill": "#E5E5EA"
                  },
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 12,
                  "padding": 24,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "1Q9Mi",
                      "name": "List Title",
                      "fill": "#1D1D1F",
                      "content": "Common markdown-it blocks I would design for",
                      "lineHeight": 1.15,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 24,
                      "fontWeight": "700"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "qlQhH",
                      "name": "List Text",
                      "fill": "#4D4D52",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": 820,
                      "content": "• H1 / H2 / H3 headings with stable spacing\n• Paragraphs with readable width and 1.7 line height\n• Blockquotes that feel distinct but not heavy\n• Code fences with monospaced typography\n• Ordered and unordered lists with generous indentation",
                      "lineHeight": 1.75,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 17
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
